<! [CDATA[
XTRABYTES (XBY) Logo XTRABYTES™️ describes itself as a blockchain platform that allows DApps to be programmed in any language. Standard blockchain environments contain many centralization vulnerabilities, such as self-contained development, consensus methods, and coin monopolization. The XTRABYTES™️ platform seeks to rectify these limitations and aims to create a truly decentralized cryptocurrency and applications platform. XTRABYTES™️ aspires to offer a next-generation blockchain solution capable of providing a diverse set of capabilities. Source
You can download theXTRABYTESlogo on full-version of the page. ]] >
